task.summary: Changed allObjects in each class to a permanent mapping in the base class, CanvasObject, where it can be called via CanvasObject.allObjects(Class <T> type) and it will return a list of all objects that are Type <T> or a subclass of <T>.

Changed allObjects in each class to a permanent mapping in the base class, CanvasObject, where it can be called via CanvasObject.allObjects(Class <T> type) and it will return a list of all objects that are Type <T> or a subclass of <T>.
Added package scanner and all classes in 'subscene' will be added to the allScenes list. NullPointer occurring in Ellipse due to either FVec dimensions or Scale.
Improved color class and shifted planar static variables to Scene1, where they should be as they are used there only.
Improved color interpolation, and now changing labelAxes() to replace static text with TextVObjects.

Successfully added wrapper classes to PApplet and PGraphics that allow further customization, such as the shortening of methods such as line(x1,y1,x2,y2) to line(FVector start, FVector end), and simply stroke(Color color) and fill(Color color).
Issue with CanvasObject.getAllObjects(Class<T> type), because it does not retrieve any canvas.line objects created.
